    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "样式都设置好了。我检查一下：start透明圆角，end紫色圆角，中间节点淡紫。supervisor到四个动作是虚线，动作回supervisor是实线，safety直通end。",
      "elements_involved": [
